{"tid":2501070,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"ITZY 〈Guess Who〉全員概念照到齊！4/30 發行今年首張專輯","createTime":"2021-04-23T06:16:40.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-23T06:20:37.000Z","uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"621ef4b225529d1741ea8c94f385daeee9b5b865","tid":2501070,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T06:16:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/800_86400_99e3627fea6c7219892f1380061b7031/static.koreastardaily.com/2021-04-23/135058-904203.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F800_86400_99e3627fea6c7219892f1380061b7031%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2021-04-23%2F135058-904203.png&h=fd995b64&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n距離 ITZY 回歸只剩一週，隨著整張專輯的風格益發明確，這次回歸也越來越令人期待！<br />\n<br />\nJYP Entertainment 最近接連公開禮志、Lia、留眞、彩領和有娜為了第四張迷你專輯〈Guess Who〉所拍的個人概念照，分成「夜晚」、「白天」兩種版本，呈現出大相徑庭但同樣華麗迷人的畫報。<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_0f8409c87956717c3e50cca30a98cad9/static.koreastardaily.com/2021-04-23/135058-904204.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_0f8409c87956717c3e50cca30a98cad9%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2021-04-23%2F135058-904204.png&h=742508d6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_6db09a4a566f9a3fba7bf5d9cba344c7/static.koreastardaily.com/2021-04-23/135058-904206.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_6db09a4a566f9a3fba7bf5d9cba344c7%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2021-04-23%2F135058-904206.jpeg&h=2d1ed130&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nITZY 從 2019 年出道便以系列作〈IT&rsquo;z Different〉、〈IT&rsquo;z Icy〉、〈IT&rsquo;z ME〉奠定了自信十足、勇於表達自我的形象，並在去年夏天用〈Not Shy〉展現邁入新層次的決心。這次 ITZY 延續強勢的路線，以朴軫永參與作詞、作曲和編曲的主打歌 &ldquo;Ma.Fi.A in the Morning&rdquo; 為首，將發表 &ldquo;Sorry not Sorry&rdquo;、&ldquo;Kidding Me&rdquo;、&ldquo;Wild Wild West&rdquo;、&ldquo;Shoot!&rdquo; 和 &ldquo;Tennis&rdquo; 共六首歌。<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_756f1974cbb70a262223b627ce091999/static.koreastardaily.com/2021-04-23/135058-904205.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_756f1974cbb70a262223b627ce091999%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2021-04-23%2F135058-904205.jpeg&h=c20d5a56&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nITZY 將於 4 月 30 日下午 1 點（韓國時間）發行〈Guess Who〉，帶來 2021 年第一次回歸。在那之前，就先來聽聽她們不久前首度發行的 fan song 吧！<br />\n<br />\n（照片或影片來源：JYP Entertainment）"},{"pid":"c3d4038a3aeef7f81657e7af828d37e2769e75f4","tid":2501070,"uid":339805,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T06:17:08.000Z","msg":"Wfc<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d539545c9d3a95b8fa7104d2bcbf61b587168d2","tid":2501070,"uid":93096,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T06:20:06.000Z","msg":"支持(2.5)....<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfe929a451ad22e7c873adf62dfe217d44f7deba","tid":2501070,"uid":261849,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T06:20:37.000Z","msg":"Who"}]}